(The Hollywood Reporter)A rebellious young woman, a sniper and an aging rocker are heading to theaters this weekend with the releases of "Insurgent," "The Gunman" and "Danny Collins."

Find out what The Hollywood Reporter's critics are saying about the weekend's new offerings (as well as which film will likely top the weekend's box office).

